"use strict";(self.webpackChunkzhishi=self.webpackChunkzhishi||[]).push([[6493],{829:(e,a,n)=>{n.r(a),n.d(a,{data:()=>s});const s={key:"v-e48c65b2",path:"/app/homebrew/",title:"Homebrew",lang:"zh-CN",frontmatter:{},excerpt:"",headers:[{level:2,title:"Homebrew",slug:"homebrew-1",children:[]}],filePathRelative:"app/homebrew/README.md",git:{updatedTime:1626626739e3,contributors:[{name:"tangxue",email:"11183504@qq.com",commits:1}]}}},648:(e,a,n)=>{n.r(a),n.d(a,{default:()=>i});var s=n(6252);const r=(0,s.Wm)("h1",{id:"homebrew",tabindex:"-1"},[(0,s.Wm)("a",{class:"header-anchor",href:"#homebrew","aria-hidden":"true"},"#"),(0,s.Uk)(" Homebrew")],-1),l=(0,s.Wm)("h2",{id:"homebrew-1",tabindex:"-1"},[(0,s.Wm)("a",{class:"header-anchor",href:"#homebrew-1","aria-hidden":"true"},"#"),(0,s.Uk)(" Homebrew")],-1),p={href:"https://brew.sh/index_zh-cn",target:"_blank",rel:"noopener noreferrer"},b=(0,s.Uk)("官网地址"),c=(0,s.uE)('<h4 id="_1-更新-homebrew" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_1-更新-homebrew" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 1. 更新 Homebrew</h4><p>要获取最新的包的列表，首先得更新 Homebrew 自己。这可以用 brew update 办到。</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code>brew update\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div><h4 id="_2-更新包-formula" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_2-更新包-formula" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 2. 更新包 (formula)</h4><p>更新之前，我会用 <code>brew outdated</code> 查看哪些包可以更新。</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code>brew outdated\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div><p>然后就可以用 <code>brew upgrade</code> 去更新了。Homebrew 会安装新版本的包，但旧版本仍然会保留。</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code><span class="token comment"># 更新所有的包</span>\nberw upgrade\n\n<span class="token comment"># 更新指定的包</span>\nbrew upgrade <span class="token variable">$FORMULA</span>    \n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br><span class="line-number">3</span><br><span class="line-number">4</span><br><span class="line-number">5</span><br></div></div><h4 id="_3-清理旧版本" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_3-清理旧版本" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 3. 清理旧版本</h4><p>一般情况下，新版本安装了，旧版本就不需要了。我会用 <code>brew cleanup</code> 清理旧版本和缓存文件。Homebrew 只会清除比当前安装的包更老的版本，所以不用担心有些包没更新但被删了。</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code><span class="token comment"># 清理所有包的旧版本</span>\nbrew cleanup\n\n<span class="token comment"># 清理指定包的旧版本</span>\nbrew cleanup <span class="token variable">$FORMULA</span>\n\n<span class="token comment"># 查看可清理的旧版本包，不执行实际操作</span>\nbrew cleanup -n\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br><span class="line-number">3</span><br><span class="line-number">4</span><br><span class="line-number">5</span><br><span class="line-number">6</span><br><span class="line-number">7</span><br><span class="line-number">8</span><br></div></div><p>这样一套下来，该更新的都更新了，旧版本也被清理了。</p><h4 id="_4-锁定不想更新的包" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_4-锁定不想更新的包" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 4. 锁定不想更新的包</h4><p>如果经常更新的话，<code>brew update</code> 一次更新所有的包是非常方便的。但我们有时候会担心自动升级把一些不希望更新的包更新了。</p><p>数据库就属于这一类，尤其是 PostgreSQL 跨 minor 版本升级都要迁移数据库的。我们更希望找个时间单独处理它。这时可用 <code>brew pin</code> 去锁定这个包，然后 <code>brew update</code> 就会略过它了。</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code><span class="token comment"># 锁定某个包</span>\nbrew pin <span class="token variable">$FORMULA</span>\n\n<span class="token comment"># 取消锁定</span>\nbrew unpin <span class="token variable">$FORMULA</span>\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br><span class="line-number">3</span><br><span class="line-number">4</span><br><span class="line-number">5</span><br></div></div><h4 id="_5-其他几个常用命令" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_5-其他几个常用命令" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 5.其他几个常用命令</h4><p>查看包的相关信息</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code><span class="token comment"># 可以查看包的相关信息，最有用的应该是包依赖和相应的命令</span>\nbrew info\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br></div></div>',19),i={render:function(e,a){const n=(0,s.up)("OutboundLink");return(0,s.wg)(),(0,s.j4)(s.HY,null,[r,l,(0,s.Wm)("p",null,[(0,s.Wm)("a",p,[b,(0,s.Wm)(n)])]),c],64)}}}}]);